bcl:text:
and includes, except in sections 2 (1), (3) and (5) and 11, a person for whom
          nomination papers for election to office as a municipal official have been
          filed;

bcl:paragraph.bcl:text:
the name of each business situated or carrying on business in British Columbia and
          financially remunerating the nominee or public employee as an owner, part owner, trustee
          or partner;

the name of each business located or carrying on business in British Columbia and
          financially remunerating the nominee or public employee for services performed by the
          person as an employee;

the name of each organization located in British Columbia and financially
          remunerating the nominee or public employee for an office held by the person that is not
          disclosed under paragraph (b) or (c);
